HEADWORD: Sciscitation
<hw>Scis`ci*ta"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>sciscitatio</ets>, fr. <ets>sciscitari</ets> to inquire, from
<ets>sciscere</ets> to seek to know, v. incho. from <ets>scire</ets> to
know.]</ety> <def>The act of inquiring; inquiry; demand.</def>
